                        sample.key_expr().as_str(),
                        payload,
                    );
                }
                Err(err) => {
                    let payload = err
                        .payload()
                        .try_to_string()
                        .unwrap_or_else(|e| e.to_string().into());
                    println!(">> Received (ERROR: '{payload}')");
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

