121	    /// Changes the Express policy to apply when routing the request.
122	    ///
123	    /// When express is set to `true`, then the message will not be batched.
124	    /// This usually has a positive impact on latency but a negative impact on throughput.
125	    fn express(self, is_express: bool) -> Self {
